		<li class="" id="comment-116112">

			
			<p class="commenter">
				<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/f758ca9a9fa756252e9aa9ce2726658b?s=32&amp;d=wavatar&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' />				By Tim  posted on <b>September 10, 2006 at 2:23 pm</b> <br />
