		<li class="" id="comment-116514">

			
			<p class="commenter">
				<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/2fc0032c933128645bb042ab3bda135d?s=32&amp;d=wavatar&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' />				By Stamp  posted on <b>September 11, 2006 at 8:18 am</b> <br />
